# ============================================================================
# Setup Instructions
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. Copy this file:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Fill in required Supabase credentials
#
# 3. Get free Google PageSpeed API key (REQUIRED)
#
# 4. Deploy database migrations:
#    supabase db push
#
# 5. Set Supabase secrets:
#    supabase secrets set PAGESPEED_INSIGHTS_API_KEY=your_key
#
# 6. Deploy edge functions:
#    supabase functions deploy
#
# 7. (Optional) Configure paid APIs for advanced features
#
# 8. Test the system:
#    Navigate to /admin/seo in your application
#
# See SEO_IMPLEMENTATION_GUIDE.md for detailed setup instructions
# ============================================================================
